  "text": "The Nourishing Lip BalmSummer Fridays Lip Butter BalmThese days, the supple, glossy sheen you notice on most lips comes courtesy of Summer Fridays’ cult-favorite lip balms. The brand’s latest iteration of its viral formula has an even pinker hue than, say, Pink Sugar or Birthday Cake, to mimic the color of the fruit’s core. The Defining Curl CreamRahua Enchanted Island Vegan Curl Butter Rahua’s curl cream is formulated with fortifying and strengthening ingredients, including biotin, African shea butter, and oils, among others, with guava as the standout. “Think less damage, more shine. It hydrates and smoothes the hair cuticle, which results in softer texture and a natural, healthy glow, all with that fresh, fruity scent lingering behind,” Anna Ayers, founder of Rahua, explains. Advertisement - Continue Reading BelowThe Hydrating Body WashKopari Hydrating Body WashVacation starts as soon as you spritz on a Kopari fan-favorite SPF formula. However, in this case, your real respite begins in-shower. Beyond the guava scent, the Hydrating Body Wash caresses the skin with calming aloe, hydrating coconut water, and antioxidant-rich sea kelp to prep your skin for a day of fun. The Silky Leave-In ConditionerCamille Rose Guava Slip Detangling Leave-InThis lightweight leave-in conditioner will help your hair achieve its silkiest, softest form. Guava extract conditions and adds sheen to every strand, while aloe vera juice and plum extract lock in hydration. Advertisement - Continue Reading BelowThe Multiuse SprayCeremonia Guava Rescue Spray Detangler And Heat ProtectantYou get the best of many worlds from this one spray. Ceremonia’s Guava Rescue Spray serves as a detangler and nourisher, while guava offers heat protection up to 450 degrees Fahrenheit. The Comfortable LipstickYves Saint Laurent Rouge Volupté Shine Lipstick Balm 214 Wet Guava Whether worn alone or paired with a lip liner, this YSL formula glides effortlessly onto the lips for a comfortable, soft-sheen finish in a light pink shade.Advertisement - Continue Reading BelowFenty Skin Butta Drop Whipped Oil Body Cream One scoop of this body cream is enough to give your skin a vacation-like glow, and its delicious scent is the cherry, uh, guava on top. As the moisturizing formula imparts a subtle sheen and softness to the skin, your body is wrapped in the scent of guava, coconut water, and gardenia. The Exfoliating Cleanser Sweet July Pava Exfoliating CleanserAyesha Curry’s Sweet July offerings are love letters to her Caribbean upbringing, and the Pava cleanser utilizes the tropic island’s star ingredients to address a bevy of skin concerns. Papaya, guava, and glycolic acid work together to gently exfoliate dead skin cells, revealing a refreshed, smoother, and more refined complexion. Advertisement - Continue Reading BelowThe Fruity-Floral JuiceMind Games Counterplay Extrait de ParfumFlorals and fruits fight for the spotlight in this fragrance, which features a medley of creamy florals ylang-ylang and osmanthus, and vibrant banana and guava for a fruity touch. The Fruit Enzymes TonerDezi Skin Leche de Guava This toner is powered by Dezi Skin’s patented Guavazyme technology, comprised of guava and pear extracts, aimed at reducing the appearance of hyperpigmentation and scarring. Advertisement - Continue Reading BelowThe Versatile Tanning Drops Ere Perez Guava Gradual Tan DropsEre Perez’s tan drops allow you to achieve a sun-kissed glow without a sunny escape. Made with vitamin C from guava and aloe vera, these drops can be mixed into your favorite serum and moisturizer, so you can wake up feeling like you’re in the tropics—without leaving home. Arquiste TropicalAs its name suggests, Tropical by Arquiste smells like a summer cocktail waiting to be indulged. Ginger anchors the juicy tang of ripe guava and lime upon first spritz, and as it settles, guava continues mingling with the notes.",
